      • getIgnoredColumnsInError

        public List<String> getIgnoredColumnsInError()
        This method returns a List of Strings. The values are the columns that were specified to be ignored in the table, but do not exist in the table.
        返回:
        a List of Strings - the columns that were improperly configured as ignored columns
